30cb\u30d0\u30fc\u30b9}}, released on March 16, 2019, alongside characters from ''[[Hugtto! PreCure]]'' and ''[[Kirakira PreCure a la Mode]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-12-18/toei-outlines-march-precure-miracle-universe-film/.140962|title=Toei Outlines March's Precure Miracle Universe Film|website=Anime News Network|language=en|accessdate=2018-12-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Hodgkins |first1=Crystalyn |title=Precure Miracle Universe Anime Film Reveals Poster Visual |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/daily-briefs/2018-12-28/precure-miracle-universe-anime-film-reveals-poster-visual/.141399 |website=Anime News Network |accessdate=February 26, 2019 |language=en |date=December 28, 2018}}</ref>\n\nAn anime film titled {{nihongo4|''Star\u2606Twinkle Precure the Movie: These Feelings Within The Song of Stars''|\u6620\u753b\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u2606\u30c8\u30a5\u30a4\u30f3\u30af\u30eb\u30d7\u30ea\u30ad\u30e5\u30a2 \u661f\u306e\u6b4c\u306b\u60f3\u3044\u3092\u3053\u3081\u3066|Eiga Sut\u0101 Touinkuru Purikyua Hoshi no Uta ni Omoi wo Komete}} was released on October 19, 2019. Y\u016bta Tanaka is directing the film.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hodgkins |first1=Crystalyn |title=Star \u2606 Twinkle Precure Anime Gets Film on October 19|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-06-02/star-twinkle-precure-anime-gets-film-on-october-19/.147388|website=Anime News Network |accessdate=June 2, 2019 |language=en |date=June 2, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Manga===\nA [[manga]] adaptation illustrated by [[Futago Kamikita]] began serialization in [[Kodansha]]'s ''[[Nakayoshi]]'' [[shoujo]] magazine from February 1, 2019.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ressler |first1=Karen |title=Hugtto! Precure Manga Ends, Star \u2606 Twinkle Precure Manga Begins in February |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-12-30/hugtto-precure-manga-ends-star-twinkle-precure-manga-begins-in-february/.141395 |website=Anime News Network |accessdate=February 26, 2019 |language=en |date=December 30, 2018}}</ref>{{notelist}}\n\n==Reception==\n''Gadget Ts\u016bshin'' listed Hikaru's catchphrase in their 2019 anime buzzwords list.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2019-12-04/demon-slayer-dr-stone-zombie-land-saga-buzzwords-make-gadget-tsushin-2019-list/.153903|title=Demon Slayer, Dr. Stone, Zombie Land Saga Buzzwords Make Gadget Ts\u016bshin 2019 List|work=[[Anime News Network]]|first1=Lynzee|last1=Loveridge|first2=Kim|last2=Morrissy|date=December 4, 2019|accessdate=December 14, 2019}}</ref>\n\nCosplay marathoner Mitsunobu Saita ran in the 2019 [[Kobe Marathon]] as Cure Cosmo.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.kobe-np.co.jp/news/sougou/201911/0012887784.shtml|title=\u795e\u6238\uff2d\u540d\u7269\u30d7\u30ea\u30ad\u30e5\u30a2\u30e9\u30f3\u30ca\u30fc\u3000\u4eca\u5e74\u306f\u300c\u30ad\u30e5\u30a2\u30b3\u30b9\u30e2\u3060\u30cb\u30e3\u30f3\uff5e\u300d\u3067\u8efd\u3005\u30b5\u30d6\uff13|work=Kobe Shimbun|language=Japanese|date=18 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.toei-anim.co.jp/tv/startwinkle_precure/ Official website] {{in lang|ja}}\n*[http://www.asahi.co.jp/precure/ Official website (Asahi)] {{in lang|ja}}\n*{{ann|anime|21719}}\n\n{{start box}}\n{{succession box\n| title = [[Pretty Cure]]\n| before = [[Hugtto! PreCure]]\n| after = [[Healin' Good PreCure]]\n| years = 2019-2020\n}}\n{{end box}}\n\n{{Pretty Cure}}\n{{Toei Animation}}\n\n[[Category:2019 anime television series]]\n[[Category:Kodansha manga]]\n[[Category:Magical girl anime and manga]]\n[[Category:Pretty Cure]]\n[[Category:Science fiction anime and manga]]\n[[Category:Sh\u014djo manga]]\n[[Category:2019 comics endings]]\n[[Category:Toei Animation television]]\n[[Category:TV Asahi shows]]\n[[Category:Television series about alien visitations]]\n[[Category:Extraterrestrial superheroes]]\n[[Category:Extraterrestrial anime and manga]]\n", "name_user": "SmashStar30", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eAnime", "url