 of coronavirus in the country. The Chinese nationals were tourists travelling to Armenia from neighbouring [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]. Liana Torosyan, the head of the Department of Infectious Diseases, advised that samples will be sent to European labs, as Armenia does not have the capacity to test for the novel coronavirus.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1002962.html|title=Two Chinese nationals placed in isolation wards in Armenia amid first suspected case of coronavirus|date=29 January 2020|website=Armenpress.am|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201155551/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1002962.html|archive-date=1 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Brazil reports a total of 9 suspected cases in six states of the country.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://g1.globo.com/bemestar/coronavirus/noticia/2020/01/29/brasil-tem-nove-casos-suspeitos-de-coronavirus-e-33-notificacoes.ghtml|title=Brasil tem 9 casos suspeitos de coronav\u00edrus em 6 estados|publisher=O Globo|location=Brazil|language=Portuguese|website=G1|access-date=2020-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129210423/https://g1.globo.com/bemestar/coronavirus/noticia/2020/01/29/brasil-tem-nove-casos-suspeitos-de-coronavirus-e-33-notificacoes.ghtml|archive-date=2020-01-29|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAir Canada is halting all direct flights to China following the federal government's advisory to avoid non-essential travel to the mainland due to the coronavirus epidemic. The suspension is effective Thursday and slated to last until February 29.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://vancouverisland.ctvnews.ca/air-canada-suspends-all-direct-flights-to-china-as-coronavirus-spreads-1.4789002|title=Air Canada suspends all direct flights to China as coronavirus spreads|date=29 January 2020|website=Vancouver Island|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201014048/https://vancouverisland.ctvnews.ca/air-canada-suspends-all-direct-f