t-sen Memorial Hall (Guangzhou)|Sun Yat-sen Memorial Hall]], [[Canton Tower]], [[Gulangyu]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202001/24/WS5e2a7999e4b0e6e58393bd21.html|title=\u53a6\u95e8\u9f13\u6d6a\u5c7f\u666f\u533a\u6536\u8d39\u666f\u70b9\u5c55\u9986\u535a\u7269\u9986\u6682\u505c\u5f00\u653e|website=www.bjd.com.cn|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125072912/http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202001/24/WS5e2a7999e4b0e6e58393bd21.html|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Yu Garden]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2020-01-24/doc-iihnzahk6100152.shtml|title=\u4e0a\u6d77\u8c6b\u56ed\u4eca\u5929\u8d77\u95ed\u56ed \u5df2\u7ecf\u7f51\u4e0a\u8d2d\u7968\u89c2\u4f17\u53ef\u7533\u8bf7\u9000\u6b3e|last=\u770b\u770b\u65b0\u95fbKNEWS|date=2020-01-24|website=news.sina.com.cn|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125072912/https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2020-01-24/doc-iihnzahk6100152.shtml|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Shanghai Disneyland Park|Shanghai Disneyland]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.shanghaidisneyresort.com/en/|title=Shanghai Disney Resort Official Site|last=|first=|date=January 24, 2020|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107223329/https://www.shanghaidisneyresort.com/en/|archive-date=November 7, 2019|access-date=}}</ref> [[West Lake]], and [[Forbidden City]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-01-24/1402696.html|title=\u5168\u56fd\u591a\u5730\u53d6\u6d88\u6587\u65c5\u6d3b\u52a8 \u591a\u4e2a\u666f\u533a\u666f\u70b9\u6682\u65f6\u5173\u95ed {{!}} \u6bcf\u7ecf\u7f51|website=www.nbd.com.cn|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200124122733/http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-01-24/1402696.html|archive-date=2020-01-24|url-status=live}}</ref> Citing the coronavirus outbreak, [[Starbucks]] and [[McDonald's]] suspended some operations in China.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://finance.yahoo.com